  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rally 9000 is a simple 3D rally game. Complete tracks as fast as possible, and unlock levels and upgrades!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game aims to deliver the best of arcade and simulation racing in one package!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Key Features:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1. Custom Level Editor!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2. Random wildlife events: wildlife may run out onto the the track at any given moment</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3. In-game shop to purchase dozens vehicle upgrades, new tracks and more!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4. Six car models</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >5. Customize car colors, and neon lighting</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >6. Complex weather systems including rain storms & snow.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >7. Day & night tracks.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >8. Damageable vehicles</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >9. Online steam leader-boards & local high scores</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >10. Fantastical tracks</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >11. Consistent bug patches</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >12. Updates with new features and tracks</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rally 9000 is a simple 3D rally game. Complete tracks as fast as possible, and unlock levels and upgrades!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game aims to deliver the best of arcade and simulation racing in one package!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Key Features:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1. Custom Level Editor!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2. Random wildlife events: wildlife may run out onto the the track at any given moment</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3. In-game shop to purchase dozens vehicle upgrades, new tracks and more!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4. Six car models</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >5. Customize car colors, and neon lighting</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >6. Complex weather systems including rain storms & snow.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >7. Day & night tracks.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >8. Damageable vehicles</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >9. Online steam leader-boards & local high scores</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >10. Fantastical tracks</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >11. Consistent bug patches</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >12. Updates with new features and tracks</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
